Psalm 120-4 <t><f>ⓒ</f> A warrior's <f>ⓓ</f>sharp arrows, </t><t>with glowing <f>ⓔ</f>coals of the broom tree! </t>
Psalm 120-5 <pb/><t>Woe to me, that I sojourn in <f>ⓕ</f>Meshech, </t><t>that I dwell among <f>ⓖ</f>the tents of <f>ⓗ</f>Kedar!</t>
Psalm 120-6 <t>Too long have I had my dwelling </t><t>among those who hate peace.</t>
Psalm 120-7 <t><f>ⓘ</f> I am for peace, </t><t>but when I speak, they are for war! </t>